Hi <@U057DHLS75W>  you can use JavaScript to add an event listener to the button that will trigger the chatbot code when the button is clicked. You can add it to the landing page itself inside script tag.
```&lt;button id="chatbot-button"&gt;Open Chatbot&lt;/button&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
  // Get the button element
  var button = document.getElementById('chatbot-button');

  // Add an event listener to the button
  button.addEventListener('click', function() {
    // Depending what chatbot you are using just add the embed code to open it here. 
  });
&lt;/script&gt;```
Or just use the HubSpot one, here how you can create and setup one:
<https://knowledge.HubSpot.com/chatflows/create-a-bot>

